text: Nikolas Sylvester (born 20 January 2000) is a Vincentian swimmer. He competed in the men's 50 metre freestyle event at the 2016 Summer Olympics, where he ranked 61st with a time of 25.64 seconds, a national record. He did not advance to the semifinals.
